Events.RelatedBody:
Enable awaiting on multiple Tasks with mixed generic types.
Another benefit from using return value of ValueTuple instead of Array, is the ability to deconstruction the return values.

Example: 
            Task<int> t1 = Task.Run(() => ANSWER);
            Task<string> t2 = Task.Run(() => QUESTION);
            (int a, string q) = await TaskPlus.WhenAllMixed(t1, t2).ConfigureAwait(false);

I'm having test for this feature but I didn't found the right place for it in the Git repo.

